Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.52,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Genshiro is your past life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:35.96,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayame tried to save Genshiro,\Nby using a spell of immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:38.90,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,But she cast the spell\Non herself by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:43.14,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she was still\Nalive up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:47.37,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the reincarnation of Genshiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:55.44,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,...and she fell in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.98,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to get old with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:04.13,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she was\Ntrying to do that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.56,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse her immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.66,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,But she failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.50,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:17.10,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, she freed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.23,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,...so she could finally die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:24.07,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's no point to what she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:28.37,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't be together,\Nher death was all for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:44.99,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:46.40,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:49.60,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not believe this but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:52.20,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Ayame in your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.44,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the reincarnation of Ayame.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:57.97,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.88,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been through some weird things but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:04.39,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,The same person can't live\Ntwo lives at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:06.32,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how it's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:12.59,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was born 19 years ago as\Nthe reincarnation of Ayame.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:17.23,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a paradox, but we shared the same\Nspirit between our two bodies at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:21.10,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to consider that as time moves\Nforward, it can also move backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:22.60,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:24.50,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:29.54,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.25,0:22:35.58,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.42,0:22:38.85,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon... Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:43.86,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for saying such unbelievable things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:45.66,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.23,0:22:47.96,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I do believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.27,0:22:53.63,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,That night, in my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:56.64,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Ayame and I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:22:59.31,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a full moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:02.44,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:04.71,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:10.28,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,If she didn't complete the\Nceremony, she would have lived?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:12.85,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,And if she had lived...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:17.76,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,...you might have ceased to exist, Maiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.36,0:23:21.52,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, even at the\Ncost of your own life...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:24.83,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried your best to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:29.43,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew what she was going to\Ndo but I couldn't let her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:31.67,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to live if I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:35.58,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you asked me that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:41.51,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Me or Ayame...\NWho's more important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.39,0:23:46.82,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.59,0:23:48.75,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted you to decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:52.39,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was most important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:23:53.96,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Maiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:23:57.99,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would believe us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:05.20,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,But we know we are the reincarnations\Nof Genshiro and Ayame.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.46,0:24:25.45,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll keep the promise made\Nover 400 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.36,0:24:27.56,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:32.03,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think my father had this\Nin mind with his last request.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.68,0:24:41.61,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Maiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.48,0:24:44.64,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Takakage...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.75,0:24:48.91,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not used to this,\Nwe don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.52,0:24:51.49,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.94,0:25:15.57,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.46,0:25:27.36,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,That feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.60,0:25:39.83,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.41,0:25:45.31,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Maiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:55.44,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Maiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.15,0:25:59.85,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, I want to be one with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.70,0:26:06.16,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Maiko, I'm going to put it in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.86,0:26:07.76,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.90,0:26:11.09,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.97,0:26:14.03,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.64,0:26:17.47,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.81,0:26:20.37,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, Maiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.52,0:26:33.11,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.92,0:26:35.98,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.46,0:26:38.93,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,But my blood is boiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.43,0:26:42.46,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hot I'm going to melt!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.57,0:26:49.03,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,More! More! Push harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.54,0:26:56.24,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No! I think I'm losing my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.41,0:27:25.84,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, brother! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.58,0:27:28.94,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.01,0:27:33.21,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.32,0:27:34.31,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Maiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.26,0:28:16.16,campus,,0000,0000,0000,,Maiko, look!
